----Q3:  2*(n-2)+1
2 person 1 trip   =  2*(2-2)+1

3 person 3 trips  =  2*(3-2)+1

4 person 5 trips  =  2*(4-2)+1

5 person 7 trips  =  2*(5-2)+1

5 person 9 trips  =  2*(6-2)+1